# TASK TRACKER CLI

## Features
- add new task
- list tasks
- filter tasks with different status
- update task
- delete task
- created and updated timestamps
- store to JSON file

## Usage
- python3 task_tracker.py <command> [args]
    ### Add
    - python3 task_tracker.py add "description"
    ### Update 
    - python3 task_tracker.py update 1 "New description"
    ### List All
    - python3 task_tracker.py list
    ### List Specific Status
    - python3 task_tracker.py list [todo, mark-in-progress, mark-done] <id>
    ### Delete
    - python3 task_tracker.py delete <id>